                        .project-details__description-wrapper
                            %p Social media for Sharelov, a marketing collaboration platform designed to streamline communication and enhance teamwork among marketing professionals.
                            %p
                                %strong Challenge:
                                How can a new marketing management software establish a recognizable brand and successfully put themselves on the map?
                            %h4 Key Takeaways
                            %ul
                                %li.c1
                                    %strong Chasing Trends:
                                    As a marketing software, it is especially important to stay ahead of industry trends. We monitored and highlighted emerging trends to ensure relevance and enhanced engagement with our audience's evolving preferences.
                                %li.c1
                                    %strong User Generated Content:
                                    Leveraging user-generated content that reflects the brand image provided an opportunity to connect with new audiences who have similar interests and aesthetics.
                                %li.c1 
                                    %strong Building Raport:
                                    Building rapport with followers on Instagram is crucial as it fosters trust and loyalty, leading to stronger relationships and increased engagement with the brand.
                                %li.c1 
                                    %strong Content Mix:
                                    We ensured a diverse range of post themes to deliver added value to our audience, including memes, highlights of new social media features, blog posts, infographics, and social media tips.
                                

